{"tid":1163318,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有幾多個住村屋嘅巴打有安裝太陽能","createTime":"2019-05-20T11:29:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T16:26:06.000Z","uid":124017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"481bb3e76aaf7f1ea8f4578fc9552d809e2dd591","tid":1163318,"uid":124017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T11:29:19.000Z","msg":"有冇已裝太陽能嘅巴打分享下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea5cc0a81d26de4b121c1403dd9a3739e7b11b7e","tid":1163318,"uid":80662,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"481bb3e76aaf7f1ea8f4578fc9552d809e2dd591","tid":1163318,"uid":124017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T11:29:19.000Z","msg":"有冇已裝太陽能嘅巴打分享下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T17:47:58.000Z","msg":"想裝,頭先fb有間公司話有3 個plan可以選擇,所以我都想問吓有冇人喺村屋裝過<br />\n<br />\n成本<br />\n安裝費<br />\n第三者保險<br />\n回報(賣返畀電力公司)<br />\n<br />\n做緊呢行巴絲可唔可幫大家解答吓<br />\n<br />\n咁呢間公司我就唔同佢賣廣告啦,<br />\n所以佢公司資料我就唔貼出嚟.<br />\n<br />\n其他資料大家可以參考吓<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n太陽能發電計畫方案<br />\n<br />\n零成本計劃<br />\n<br />\n* \t\t業主零投資，享30%發電收益<br />\n<br />\n* \t\t建造成本100%由日兆投資<br />\n<br />\n* \t\t即裝即用，零回本期*<br />\n<br />\n* \t\t15年免費維修保養*<br />\n<br />\n* \t\t24小時監控系統<br />\n<br />\n* \t\t於首十二個月內，業主可原價購買整套發電系統*<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1+1合資計劃<br />\n<br />\n* \t\t業主投資30%<br />\n<br />\n* \t\t分期付款減輕負擔<br />\n<br />\n* \t\t回本期短<br />\n<br />\n* \t\t15年維修保養*<br />\n<br />\n* \t\t24小時監控系統�<br />\n<br />\n100%投資保證計劃<br />\n<br />\n* \t\t客戶自資擁有系統<br />\n<br />\n* \t\t業主享有100%能源發電收益<br />\n<br />\n* \t\t15年太陽能板保養*<br />\n<br />\n* \t\t15年逆變器保養*<br />\n<br />\n* \t\t24小時監控系統<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2018可再生能源上網電費計劃<br />\n<br />\n為對抗氣候變化及推廣綠色明天，自2018年10月1日(中電)/ 2019年1月1日(港燈)起， 太陽能發電擁有人可以每度電港幣3至5元(視乎發電規模) 出售生產之電力予兩電，此價格比現時之每度電收費港幣1至1.5元高出很多。<br />\n此計劃為期15年直至2033年，鎖定太陽能發電系統投資回本期為7年，這樣擁有人就可穩定賺取另外8年的高價電費(年回報率約14%)，及後繼續賺取正常電費。<br />\n中電公告:  <a href=\"https://www.clp.com.hk/zh/community-and-environment/renewable-schemes/feed-in-tariff\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.clp.com.hk%2Fzh%2Fcommunity-and-environment%2Frenewable-schemes%2Ffeed-in-tariff&d=RsYziF%2F%2FwXRI7aJQ3s5lGUqdoMPUcUEfVTbHbk%2Bo2EU%3D&h=540fb877\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.clp.com.hk/zh/community-and-environment/renewable-schemes/feed-in-tariff</a><br />\n<br />\n中電宣傳片:  <a href=\"https://youtu.be/Dv_7m4l4uaE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDv_7m4l4uaE&d=RsYziF%2F%2FwXRI7aJQ3s5lGUqdoMPUcUEfVTbHbk%2Bo2EU%3D&h=e1b7f954\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Dv_7m4l4uaE</a><br />\n<br />\n港燈公告: <a href=\"https://www.hkelectric.com/zh/customer-services/smart-power-services\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkelectric.com%2Fzh%2Fcustomer-services%2Fsmart-power-services&d=RsYziF%2F%2FwXRI7aJQ3s5lGUqdoMPUcUEfVTbHbk%2Bo2EU%3D&h=ae94c6ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkelectric.com/zh/customer-services/smart-power-services</a>"},{"pid":"271cb972f2e9fa870530cfddefa47281c36cf710","tid":1163318,"uid":80662,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T17:49:43.000Z","msg":"一般有3個計劃<br />\n<br />\nFull pay Plan<br />\n$14萬 20塊板 <br />\n (客人需負責第三者責任保險及包料保養維修）每年$2400 一共15年<br />\n<br />\n0首期分期供款<br />\n客人申請時繳一萬手續費（中電不成功可退回）<br />\n申請批出後可以每月$3688 分60期（5年）供款<br />\n (客人需負責第三者責任保險及包料保養維修）每年$2400<br />\n<br />\n$0 Plan <br />\n客人需繳$10000申請費用（包括律師合約費、文件費等），中電申請不成功可退回<br />\n上網電價3、7分帳，公司佔7成<br />\n合約期內本公司包括一切維修及第三者責任保險"},{"pid":"2c87256eb708f21c2fc4cb88d33847e9e614970c","tid":1163318,"uid":80662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T17:57:29.000Z","msg":"自己只係想揀full pay plan<br />\n絕對唔會同興建太陽能既公司瓜分電源<br />\n<br />\n出post純粹想問吓一般一個1500 尺既天台<br />\n整個system 需要成本係幾多?<br />\n有冇巴絲喺村屋天台裝過太陽能系統?"},{"pid":"78110b2980c0c1a48e8aedfd1a47cd51